","language":"CN"},{"id":2,"name":"JoyCode","dateTime":"2025-02-10 17:41:33","actionType":"Optimized Code","content":"优化后的代码如下：

```java
@Override
public Integer getSonDefinitionId(DataResourceCatalogReleaseStageInstance instance) {
    // 构建查询条件
    LambdaQueryWrapper<DataResourceCatalogReleaseJobConfigSnapshot> wrapper = new LambdaQueryWrapper<>();
    wrapper.eq(DataResourceCatalogReleaseJobConfigSnapshot::getBaseInfoId, instance.getBaseInfoId())
           .eq(DataResourceCatalogReleaseJobConfigSnapshot::getValidateFlag, Constant.DB_BOOLEAN_FLAG_Y);

    // 获取发布配置快照
    DataResourceCatalogReleaseJobConfigSnapshot releaseSnapshot = releaseJobConfigSnapshotMapper.selectOne(wrapper);
    if(releaseSnapshot == null) {
        return null;
    }

    // 获取作业配置快照
    DataResourceCatalogJobConfigSnapshot snapshot = jobConfigSnapshotMapper.selectById(releaseSnapshot.getJobConfigSnapshotId());

    // 解析并排序定义ID列表
    List<Integer> definitionIds = new JSONArray(snapshot.getDefinitionJsonArrayStr())..toJavaList(Integer.class);
    definitionIds.sort(Integer::compareTo);

    // 查找当前定义ID的下一个ID
    int currentIndex = definitionIds.indexOf(instance.getDefinitionId());
    if (currentIndex == -1 || currentIndex + 1 >= definitionIds.size()) {
        return null;
    }

    return definitionIds.get(currentIndex + 1);
}
```

优化点：
1. 使用`JSONArray.toJavaList(Integer.class)`直接将JSONArray转换为Integer列表，简化了循环处理。
2. 使用`Integer::compareTo`作为排序比较器，简化了排序逻辑。
3. 检查定义ID是否存在于列表中，并确保当前索引有下一个元素，避免`IndexOutOfBoundsException`。

